        <div class="msgSubject">The Thaumaturge Guide</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-08-20 02:11:07 | Edited: Dec 08 2010  2:09pm  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1282291867193441649" id="quote-1282291867193441649" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1282291867193441649" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1282291867193441649&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1282291867193441649" onclick="followToggle('add','1282291867193441649')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
