in Leggings (+13 HP, +13 MP)  <br />Rank 19 - Dodoskin Leggings (+16 HP, +16 MP)  <br />Rank 29 - Leather Leggings (+20 HP, +20 MP)  <br />Rank 39 - Toadskin Leggings (+25 HP, +25 MP)  <br /> <br />Waist:  <br /> <br />Rank 21 - Leather Satchel Belt (+7 MP)  <br />Rank 31 - Tarred Leather Satchel Belt (+8 MP)  <br /> <br />Ear:  <br />Nothing gives boosts to magic stats. Use to give yourself extra defense and evasion.  <br /> <br />Finger:  <br /> <br />Rank 2 - Bone Ring (+2 Mag Acc)  <br />Rank 31 - <a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050008" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050008">Lapis Lazuli Ring (+5 MND)</a>  <br />Rank 31 - <a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050010" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050010">Malachite Ring (+5 PIE)</a>  <br />Rank 31 - <a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050012" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.zam.com/en/item.html?ffxivitem=9050012">Danburite Ring (+5 INT)</a> <br />Rank 32 - Pearl Ring (+4 Mag Acc)  <br />Rank 37 - Black Pearl Ring (+5 Mag Acc)  <br />Rank 41 - Aquamarine Ring (+7 INT)  <br />Rank 41 - Peridot Ring (+7 MND)  <br /> <br />Neck:  <br /> <br />Rank 9 - Copper Choker (+2 Mag Potency)  <br />Rank 10 - Brass Choker (+3 Mag Potency)  <br />Rank 29 - Silver Choker (+5 Mag Potency)  <br />Rank 32 - Lapis Lazuli Choker (+2 INT)  <br />Rank 32 - Malachite Choker (+2 MND)  <br />Rank 39 - Electrum Choker (+6 Mag Potency)  <br />Rank 42 - Aquamarine Choker (+3 INT)  <br />Rank 42 - Peridot Choker (+3 MND)  <br />Rank 49 - Mythril Choker (+7 Mag Potency)  <br /> <br />Wrist:  <br /> <br />Rank 14 - Bone Armilla (+13 MP)  <br />Rank 33 - Lapis Lazuli Bracelet (+6 HP, +2 INT)  <br />Rank 33 - Malachite Bracelet (+6 HP, +2 MND)  <br />Rank 34 - Pearl Bracelet (+19 MP)  <br />Rank 36 - White Coral Wristband (+13 HP, +13 MP)  <br />Rank 39 - Black Pearl Bracelet (+21 MP)  <br />Rank 41 - Blue Coral