br />Driven by Faith II <br />Converts PIE +10 into VIT +10 <br /> <br />Will to Power II <br />Converts INT +10 into STR +10 <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Aug 29th 2010  2:13pm by EdyNOTB </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179">Loadstone Profile</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649">Thaumaturge Guide</a> <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1229110.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
